{"tid":922673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何妨天真 想想 總有日可再一起","createTime":"2018-11-30T14:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T14:51:26.000Z","uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a72e47c2ed58abf822c6a7d6b8556fa94f5b9d10","tid":922673,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"我心底仲覺得我地係會一齊返<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對唔住<br />\n其實我嘅存在就係錯誤 <br />\n我根本唔應該拍拖 唔應該害人 <br />\n點解我F4嗰年無跳到落去 <br />\n如果死咗咪咩事都無 係咪<br />\n識到你係好開心 係好幸福 你一直抑鬱嘅我見到世界有希望 我每次頹 你都陪住我過 但係最尾都係被我傷害咗 <br />\n心理缺憾唔係藉口 我知啊<br />\n所以對唔住<br />\n我就係咁撚有問題<br />\n我就係一個問題<br />\n哈<br />\n屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec3e121113aa18a1f3ba0b774095a5bc740c62b","tid":922673,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"on9樓主"},{"pid":"ae55731d36147cb2ba27877f9338907300144435","tid":922673,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"點解唔去死"},{"pid":"729c606c21fd46e47059cf2071b40441ec6f3b90","tid":922673,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好死"},{"pid":"4a37f858c3c7dfff785c89d7c2f593b4669eea4f","tid":922673,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"死咗咩事都無"},{"pid":"78ee403082b396fdcd819d7813ec87da1c4a9a9b","tid":922673,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"76a8a10e5ddf56bcb06372d9df6430945c6bbe4f","tid":922673,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母</span>"},{"pid":"a104bfad7cbc737c492bc934c9d54fa8f40e6afc","tid":922673,"uid":204700,"like":0,"di